name: Jam Nutella Drop Biscuits Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: jar strawberry jam (or marmalade, or Nutella)

recipeInstructions.text: Allow butter to stand at room temperature to become soft before you start baking. Cream butter and sugar in a mixer until smooth.
Add condensed milk and combine with a wooden spoon or spatula.
Gradually add sifted flour and custard powder and combine into a dough consistency.
Roll balls of dough between your fingers to make balls of a 10c coin sized and place on a lined baking tray.
Poke balls with the narrow end of a wooden spoon to make a hole and fill biscuits with your favourite jam or Nutella.
Bake in 180 degree oven for 10 mins or until they start to turn golden brown around the edges. Yields approx 100 biscuits.
